<br>
Gallair. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ujulesbrown.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jules Brown</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/30/01 7:08:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: In the same boat as you are...</span><hr size=1> The only per-hit bonus you get is your level bonus.  Period.<br>
<br>
Strength does NOT raise your per-hit bonus.<br>
<br>
So no matter whether you have a fast weapon or slow weapon, Strength does nothing.<br>
<br>
Here is what strength does in melee versus blues (simplified):  You have like a 1% chance of hitting a mob for MAX damage.  If your strength is higher, that 1 swing in 100 will hit a little harder.  All the other 99 hits will be UNAFFECTED by your strength.<br>
<br>
That is why strength sucks (VS Blues).<br>
<br>
On reds, there is some justification for raising strength.  But reds = raiding.  Raiding = big buffs.  So who cares.<br>
<br>
Cheers,<br>
Jules <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=11954.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=11950.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=11947.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=11947.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11947.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11947.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="paladinsofnorrathgeneral">General<option value="paladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests">Holy Swords and Quests<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm8">Epic Quests<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm9">Paladin Polls<option value="paladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge">Tomes of Knowledge(read only)<option value="paladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion">Class Discussion<option value="paladinsofnorrathgodsmightroleplaytavern">God's Might(Roleplay Tavern)<option va